## 3. üí≥ Solana Wallet Setup

### Step 1: Install Phantom Wallet
1. Go to [phantom.app](https://phantom.app)
2. Install browser extension or mobile app
3. Create new wallet or import existing
4. **Save your seed phrase securely!**

### Step 2: Get Devnet SOL (Free Testing)
1. Switch Phantom to **Devnet** (Settings ‚Üí Change Network)
2. Copy your wallet address
3. Go to [solfaucet.com](https://solfaucet.com)
4. Request free devnet SOL

### Step 3: Export Private Key for Admin Wallet
1. In Phantom, go to Settings ‚Üí Export Private Key
2. Enter password
3. Copy the private key (keep it secret!)

### Step 4: Update .env File
```env
# Blockchain Configuration
SOLANA_NETWORK=devnet
SOLANA_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com
SOLANA_ADMIN_WALLET=your_private_key_here
PHANTOM_APP_ID=rize-job-portal
```

